Articles.Content:
This is my first try on making this legendary airplane and it might be my first craft I've posted here.

[http://www.filedropper.com/concorde](http://www.filedropper.com/concorde)

![F58B1997672D7D683CCA724722F8BDA9B8A3AADD](http://images.akamai.steamusercontent.com/ugc/28489013024402408/F58B1997672D7D683CCA724722F8BDA9B8A3AADD/)

It can reach nominal speed and value for Concorde.

![175B202E1A2FDEFF32B3CF8CA418D148627A029D](http://images.akamai.steamusercontent.com/ugc/28489013024435841/175B202E1A2FDEFF32B3CF8CA418D148627A029D/)

![0E521BDA69799A10BCCFCA04541B631C888A492C](http://images.akamai.steamusercontent.com/ugc/28489013024485600/0E521BDA69799A10BCCFCA04541B631C888A492C/)

It has enough lift to safely land. It's by no means a perfect or finished product so use it with caution.
